description: Akos Piros, Kevin Cage, and Tom Ryan are all sitting around in the cigar lounge patiently awaiting their entertainment: the raunchy seductions of Will Faust. With a massive black dildo, his own fist, and the piss of his onlookers, Will gives a raunchy show none are soon to forget.
title: Will Faust's Cigar Room Raunch-Fest
